name: coolwolf #13
description:
In the world of fury there is a clan of cool wolf. They have a duty
to kill the evil sheep. They are a clan of sheep who seek to rule 
the world of fury with covert cruelty. Clan of sheep that
look friendly but are actually very dangerous, they are not 
ordinary sheep. They like to eat other creatures without many 
people knowing because of their sweet and innocent appearance.
Cool wolf clan knows about their existence and they are trying 
to stop their savagery in the fury world.
